{"tid":710952,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動物朋友不死？《動物朋友RPG》B站視頻萬次突破","createTime":"2018-06-21T07:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T07:51:04.000Z","uid":179081,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b00fb047b2a97adbb65f94e8cc387bbc68ae0847","tid":710952,"uid":179081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/144439_86a36c45ae67237e261c194a64027dc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F144439_86a36c45ae67237e261c194a64027dc8.png&h=c2a5d662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝大家協力轉發！<br />\n《けものフレンズRPG》B站視頻播放突破一萬人次！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《けものフレンズRPG》，為獸娘動物園同人遊戲；<br />\n是幾乎僅以一人之人以網路既有素材製作而成的3DRPG；<br />\n各種巧思以及到位的畫面渲染，多位聲優與音樂製作者的協力<br />\n在推特上受到數萬人的關注，<br />\nNicoNico釋出的視頻也屢屢突破10萬播放，<br />\n是目前最受矚目的同人作品之一。<br />\n作者Naby目前已經釋出多語言化的意願。當然，也包含中文化！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※特別聲明<br />\n《けものフレンズRPG》是非官方的同人創作，由Naby所製作<br />\n完成時將免費發佈，並不打算進行販售。<br />\n作者推特<a href=\"https://twitter.com/7u_naby\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F7u_naby&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8f1bc7fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/7u_naby</a><br />\n作者Nico<a href=\"http://www.nicovideo.jp/mylist/59058365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nicovideo.jp%2Fmylist%2F59058365&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=50b0b0e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nicovideo.jp/mylist/59058365</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/150456_13f50b324ab879d1440e769167dd73c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F150456_13f50b324ab879d1440e769167dd73c9.png&h=7759a191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了讓更多人體會到《けものフレンズRPG》的樂趣。<br />\n同人社團」Friends Mind」，<br />\n已透過日本朋友與作者Naby電郵保持友好的交流，<br />\n取得搬運及期刊專欄等諸項授權。<br />\n旨在推廣《けものフレンズRPG》：<br />\n包括（Nico高質化展示視頻搬運、推特訊息中文化、實機實況、<br />\n遊戲多語言化(俄 西 德暨多語系)、遊戲介紹專欄、論壇與社群宣傳）等事項。<br />\n<br />\n若您願一同為了加帕里鳴鬥，<br />\n請私訊QQ號2143376522。<br />\n<br />\n最新消息：<br />\n推特　<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JapariArk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJapariArk&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c7661954\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JapariArk</a><br />\n臉書　<a href=\"https://fb.com/japariart\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fjapariart&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=047acd6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/japariart</a><br />\nBili　<a href=\"https://space.bilibili.com/2539936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspace.bilibili.com%2F2539936&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fbba83f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://space.bilibili.com/2539936</a><br />\n微博　<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/FriendsMind\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2FFriendsMind&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bcfc86d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/FriendsMind</a>"},{"pid":"7e8aea5b7714e97a83d6a75e0b0ea63b606db216","tid":710952,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國"},{"pid":"11738b7029a82def0df90ce4b51a33e7bd9bebc8","tid":710952,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"動漫台都是中國人"}]}